bud-data222: Expenditure on the dissemination of information and on participation in public events
bud-data exprev: This appropriation is intended to cover the cost of organising study days on the activities of the Court of Auditors
amounts: for the benefit of university teachers
amount: editors of specialised journals or other specialist visitors from the Member States. This appropriation is also intended to cover miscellaneous expenditure relating to the Court’s information and communication policy.
